<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="57" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,150,551]" pageId="2" pageNumber="57">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,329,301,327]" pageId="2" pageNumber="57">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Body brownish grey, with darker lateral side and green underside in life. Head orange with brownish black face (
<figureCitation box="[413,484,338,364]" captionStart="FIGURES 1 – 4" captionStartId="1.[151,272,1937,1961]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,1165,1905]" captionTargetId="figure@1.[151,1436,1165,1913]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURES 1 – 4. Amusurgus (Usgmona) genji Furukawa, 1970. 1. face, frontal view; 2. dorsal field of male tegmen, dorsal view; 3. genitalia of male, dorsal view; 4. genitalia of male, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/194525/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="57">
Fig. 
<number box="[470,484,338,364]" pageId="2" pageNumber="57" value="1.0">1</number>
</figureCitation>
), tegmen with veins lighter than cells. Eyes vertically lengthened, 
<number box="[1300,1313,338,364]" pageId="2" pageNumber="57" value="5.0">5</number>
th joint of maxillary palpi triangular. Anterior tibiae without tympanum, veins of male tegmen as in 
<figureCitation box="[1282,1360,376,402]" captionStart="FIGURES 1 – 4" captionStartId="1.[151,272,1937,1961]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,1165,1905]" captionTargetId="figure@1.[151,1436,1165,1913]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURES 1 – 4. Amusurgus (Usgmona) genji Furukawa, 1970. 1. face, frontal view; 2. dorsal field of male tegmen, dorsal view; 3. genitalia of male, dorsal view; 4. genitalia of male, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/194525/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="57">
Fig. 
<number box="[1341,1360,376,402]" pageId="2" pageNumber="57" value="2.0">2</number>
</figureCitation>
. Male genitalia as in 
<figureCitation box="[321,433,413,439]" captionStart="FIGURES 1 – 4" captionStartId="1.[151,272,1937,1961]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,1165,1905]" captionTargetId="figure@1.[151,1436,1165,1913]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURES 1 – 4. Amusurgus (Usgmona) genji Furukawa, 1970. 1. face, frontal view; 2. dorsal field of male tegmen, dorsal view; 3. genitalia of male, dorsal view; 4. genitalia of male, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/194525/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="57">
Figs. 
<number box="[386,433,413,439]" pageId="2" pageNumber="57" value="3.5" valueMax="4.0" valueMin="3.0">3–4</number>
</figureCitation>
.
</paragraph>
